This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis. The use of LSTM models also suggests that it could belong to "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) and "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves classification tasks, which could place it in the "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) sub-category. Finally, the use of neural networks and deep learning techniques could also suggest that it belongs to the "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category.
